      "author": "SecondBrainProd",
      "description": "## What's Changed\n* **Security**: Replaced innerHTML with textContent for button labels to prevent potential XSS.\n* **Compatibility**: Replaced non-standard `String.contains()` with standard ES6 `String.includes()`.\n* **Data Integrity**: Added data validation when loading history and presets from `data.json` to prevent crashes from corrupted config files.\n* **Robustness**: Added optional chaining and `filter(Boolean)` when reading metadata cache tags. Fixed command IDs cleanup on unload.",
      "downloadCount": 12,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v1.1.2: Security & Stability Improvements",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-03-05T09:23:45Z",
