      "author": "SecondBrainProd",
      "description": "## What's Changed\n* **Localization (i18n)**: Added multi-language support (English, Russian, German, Spanish, French). The plugin now automatically detects your system language. You can also manually select the language at the top of the settings page.\n* **Bug Fix**: Fixed an issue where the suggestions dropdown (for folders/tags) allowed selecting the same item multiple times. Already selected items are now filtered out.\n* **Updated Screenshots**: Replaced images in the README with the latest localized UI.",
